    issue.ext-affects: affect short names (kShortDesc -> affected_bits) and ListOneChar aura look text,
    one <msg_sheaf> per affect. The shared kDefault sheaf holds the merged shield/aura line structure:
    kShieldFrame/kAuraFrame are fmt templates ({list} = joined fragments, {noun} = count-picked noun).
    For standalone affects (cocoon/glow/status) kLook is a complete "...line "; for grouped affects
